'''Ibki''' (qqaren daɣ iddew, aḥallum) d aɣersiw asaṭṭaḍ, seg usellun  n [[iprimaṭen]], yettɛic deg waddagen s umata. Udem-is d abejliṭ, aqerru-s yemhez ddeqs-is, iɣallen-is ɣezzifit s yiḍuḍan deg ixafawen-nsen. D acu ɣas akken yezga yessawham amek i ittemcabi s amdan, assaɣ meqqren yellan iɣersiwen-a d telmest talsant ur t-id-tufa tussna armi ɛeddan leqrun.
